  ('Grade 12 English culminates in ___.',['completed study of English','the end of reading and writing as serious pursuits','only exam preparation','a genuine transformation — students who engage deeply emerge as fundamentally different readers and thinkers, with analytical skills, literary knowledge, and communicative power that will serve them throughout their lives'],3),
